      <t>&lt;p&gt;There is a need for vendor-specific extensions to Mobility Header messages so that Mobile IPv6 vendors are able to extend the protocol for research or deployment purposes.  This document defines a new vendor-specific mobility option. [STANDARDS-TRACK]&lt;/p&gt;</t>
